{"tid":2010094,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧穎芝千字文鬧爆「鹹豬手」教練借上堂非禮女學員：簡直禽獸不如","createTime":"2020-05-10T08:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T08:34:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07df76177f251f641412f8bae47dbf054ad77b53","tid":2010094,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"藝人鄧穎芝（Vangie）今日（10日）網上發火，以千字文狠批一名聲稱自己是MMA（綜合格鬥）的男教練。事緣該名教練以教格鬥技巧為名，非禮為實，借機向女學員「抽水」，而且動作相當大膽。鄧穎芝截圖留下了這名教練的罪證，更形容這位教練絕對不是真的教練，只是一名猥瑣佬。她說：「你教乜嘢武術呢請問？請廣傳，以免更多人受害！！！！！！！」然後又指，如果該名教練將相片刪除，她會再公開事先已準備好的截圖。<br />\n<br />\n鄧穎芝續說：「没有任何武術或運動，教授時需要咁多、咁貼近、咁誇張嘅身體接觸，是。没。有！ 特別係男教練（教）女學生，專業嘅教練識得尊重和避忌，而佢地亦會有相應嘅訓練去以盡量少嘅身體接觸嚟教你，如果要掂到你都會問一聲先，當有可能要掂到你啲比較敏感嘅部位，都會用其他嘢代替手，唔會直接摸你，更加唔會咁樣壓你埋牆，成個身貼住你。」<br />\n<br />\n「你覺得唔舒服已經係界線，就算你當時好驚無鬧佢，都盡快走，同身邊嘅人講，唔好再返去。 唔好比人呃，無人會咁教你，如果你真係對你教練行為有疑問，我歡迎你問我，千祈唔好啞忍呢種對待。 至於呢個猥瑣佬（佢絕對唔係一個教練，不管係知識上定態度上），我希望佢快啲去死，利用別人嘅信任去逞自己嘅淫慾，簡直禽獸不如。如果你識呢個人，或曾身受其害，可以嘅話請你出嚟指證佢。」<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》致電給了Vangie，她得知這個消息是在朋友社交網站看見的，看完後Vangie第一時間是感到慣怒，原因是她曾遇上過同類型的事年，她說：「我自己有經歷過類似事情，都係學MMA。個一刻我都係好驚，唔識處理呢件事，所以我睇到好嬲。」事後Vangie並沒有報警處理，因為那時她身在的地方是在泰國習訓，所以第二天再沒有到那個地方學MMA。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4464007/org/fccb79de82b210934d4a3081f0fa8cbb.jpg/soZOj1kbmJxBBo-0Lt4DZPhPw_1W5HKYXTulnF07pZw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4464007%2Forg%2Ffccb79de82b210934d4a3081f0fa8cbb.jpg%2FsoZOj1kbmJxBBo-0Lt4DZPhPw_1W5HKYXTulnF07pZw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=dc6c7c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4463686/org/adb7ed65173a904ca4a1c961edeb9bd2.jpg/QNHSNAkao_eEvOj_sf2IqQ2-0eunRfCfLTcFRy03BUc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4463686%2Forg%2Fadb7ed65173a904ca4a1c961edeb9bd2.jpg%2FQNHSNAkao_eEvOj_sf2IqQ2-0eunRfCfLTcFRy03BUc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c4395d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4463691/org/4eee37f0faf37c2996597720914c01d7.jpg/7aHDBYqj8vlherwdgbOQbqnTczh-F7erAeRtUgHkbVI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4463691%2Forg%2F4eee37f0faf37c2996597720914c01d7.jpg%2F7aHDBYqj8vlherwdgbOQbqnTczh-F7erAeRtUgHkbVI&h=e4803d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4463694/org/37624d6e8f02f906ab90d917f553de15.jpg/prYBxd_bpwVNzGPRcJmoRqW0hLMAhhRLxaQamcWkGpk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4463694%2Forg%2F37624d6e8f02f906ab90d917f553de15.jpg%2FprYBxd_bpwVNzGPRcJmoRqW0hLMAhhRLxaQamcWkGpk&h=c7fc403f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53468fee29d09a85a9a3348c348397ad95475191","tid":2010094,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"個教練好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517ef7309b4ac69d67908d37fd7a59b36357c584","tid":2010094,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"MMA脫髮怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06e8f99fc23539e5a6dbf6fe1a381ec626ca0b8","tid":2010094,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"佢衰係樣衰度"},{"pid":"a4132ea628ec3e71cd9b8221cfe305b5939f1192","tid":2010094,"uid":137451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"武術教練？！成個on9仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55c1011bc88b21bde0514220cf8e16fdc3d45a6","tid":2010094,"uid":41352,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"如果佢生到成個希哥咁嘅樣，我覺得個教練會桃李滿門"},{"pid":"23c64aae94978d98fb82e0c7d63a81c5bcd8206f","tid":2010094,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"想睇個女學員嘅enjoy樣"},{"pid":"fda84a63e8bc2284a1cdd430a795b